'''Gujarat State Energy Generation Ltd'''. ('''GSEG''') is a power company in Gujarat, India. It is a subsidiary of [[Gujarat State Petroleum Corporation]].<ref>{{cite web|title=GSEG|url=http://www.gspcgroup.com/company_detail.php?CID=5}}</ref> The company is engaged in gas based generation of electricity. Starting from 1 June  2000 it operates a 156&nbsp;MW [[combined cycle]] [[power plant]] near [[Hazira]], [[Surat]].

